style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>“Electronic benefit transfer” (EBT) means the
method of issuing SNAP benefits to an account, which is accessed by a recipient
with a debit card.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

