<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:-1.2pt;margin-bottom:
0in;margin-left:.75in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>(1)&nbsp;&nbsp;Earned
<span class=GramE>income that</span> varies from month-to-month such as when an
individual works varying hours, overtime, or on a piece-work basis; or</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:"Courier New";
color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>&nbsp;</span><span
