style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>(2)&nbsp;&nbsp;Unearned
<span class=GramE>income that</span> varies from month-to-month due to changes
in frequency or amount.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:"Courier New";color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

