class=GramE>Short-term, but</span>&nbsp;will last long enough to affect at
least one issuance of SNAP benefits.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
