font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>(h)<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;Verification&quot; means the use of <span
class=GramE>third party</span> documentation or <span class=GramE>third party</span>
information to establish the accuracy of statements by an individual to the
department.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

