mandatory sanction,</span> pursuant to 7 CFR 273.7(f)(2) and (j)(3)(vi), <span
style='color:black'>shall be applied as follows:</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

