<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-1.45pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:
30.25pt .75in 77.75pt 102.25pt 1.75in 149.75pt 210.25pt'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-1.2pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:
30.25pt .75in 77.75pt 102.25pt 1.75in 149.75pt 210.25pt'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><span
style='mso-tab-count:1'>          </span>(a)<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>An individual determined to be a fleeing felon, as defined in He-W
701.02(a), shall be an ineligible </span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>household</span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> member. Pursuant
to 7 CFR 273.11(n)(1)(<span class=SpellE>i</span>), the department shall
establish an individual as a fleeing felon through a four-part test:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:-1.45pt;margin-bottom:
0in;margin-left:30.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:30.25pt .75in 77.75pt 102.25pt 1.75in 149.75pt 210.25pt'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:-1.45pt;margin-bottom:
0in;margin-left:.75in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:30.25pt .75in 77.75pt 102.25pt 1.75in 149.75pt 210.25pt'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(1)<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>There is an outstanding felony warrant for
the individual by a federal, state, or local law enforcement agency, and the
underlying cause for the warrant is for committing or attempting to commit a
crime that is a felony under the law of the place from which the individual is
fleeing or a high misdemeanor under the law of New Jersey;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-1.45pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:
30.25pt .75in 77.75pt 102.25pt 1.75in 149.75pt 210.25pt'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:-1.45pt;margin-bottom:
0in;margin-left:.75in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:30.25pt .75in 77.75pt 102.25pt 1.75in 149.75pt 210.25pt'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(2)<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>The individual is aware of, or should
reasonably have been able to expect that, the felony <span class=GramE>warrant</span>
has already or would have been issued;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-1.45pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:
30.25pt .75in 77.75pt 102.25pt 1.75in 149.75pt 210.25pt'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:-1.45pt;margin-bottom:
0in;margin-left:.75in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:30.25pt .75in 77.75pt 102.25pt 1.75in 149.75pt 210.25pt'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(3)<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>The individual has taken some action to avoid
being arrested or jailed; and</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-right:-1.45pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:
30.0pt 78.0pt 102.0pt 1.75in 150.0pt 210.0pt'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:-1.45pt;margin-bottom:
0in;margin-left:48.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;tab-stops:30.0pt 78.0pt 102.0pt 1.75in 150.0pt 210.0pt'><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(4)<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>The federal, state, or local law enforcement
agency is actively seeking the individual pursuant to 7 CFR 273.11(n)(3).</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:-1.2pt;margin-bottom:
