style='color:black'> child is currently included as a member of another SNAP
household, hereinafter known as household y,&nbsp;the&nbsp;<span class=SpellE>casehead</span>&nbsp;of
SNAP household x shall provide to the department&nbsp;one of the following
documents:</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
