style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>(1)&nbsp;&nbsp;If
the child is under the age of 18, a signed statement from the&nbsp;<span
class=SpellE>casehead</span>&nbsp;of SNAP household y which states the child
resides in SNAP household x; or</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:-1.2pt;margin-bottom:
