style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>(2)&nbsp;&nbsp;If
the child is at least age 18 but under the age of 22, a signed statement from
the child stating the child resides in SNAP household x.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
